  "scenarioDescription": "\n  <ul class=\"exoplanets-navigation-menu\">\n  <li><button href=\"#system\">System</button>\n  <li><button href=\"#Proxima Cen\">Star</button>\n  <li><button href=\"#Proxima Cen-b\">b</button></li>\n  </ul>\n  <h1 id=\"system\">The Proxima Cen Exoplanetary System</h1>\n  <p>The Proxima Cen system contains 1 exoplanet. It is located 4.24 light years away from the solar system.</p>\n    <div class=\"celestial-object-wrapper\" id=\"Proxima Cen\">\n  <section>\n  <h2>Star</h2>\n  <div class=\"size-comparison-wrapper\">\n  <div class=\"celestial-sphere\" style=\"width: 100px; height: 100px; background-color: rgb(255, 242.3979365143785, 230.54885609599933);\">\n    <label>Sun</label>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"celestial-sphere\" style=\"width: 14.000000000000002px; height: 14.000000000000002px; background-color: rgb(255, 178.84444807285138, 113.33760982780717)\">\n<label>Proxima Cen</label>\n</div>\n</div>\n  </section>\n  <table cellspacing=\"0\">\n  <tr>\n    <td>Mass</td>\n    <td>0.12 solar masses</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n    <td>Radius</td>\n    <td>0.14 solar radiae</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n    <td>Temperature</td>\n    <td>3050 kelvin</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n    <td>Stellar Metallicity</td>\n    <td>- decimal exponent</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n    <td>Age</td>\n    <td>- billion years</td>\n  </tr>\n</table>\n</div>\n     \n    <div class=\"celestial-object-wrapper\" id=\"Proxima Cen-b\">\n      <section>\n        <h2>Proxima Cen-b</h2>\n        <p>At less than 1.5 Earth masses, Proxima Cen b is a terrestrial planet, much like the terrestrial planets we find in our solar system, namely Mercury, Venus, Earth and Mars.      Proxima Cen b orbits within the habitable zone of its parent star and could, potentially, be a habitable planet with stable bodies of liquid water on its surface, like Earth.</p>\n        <div class=\"size-comparison-wrapper\">\n          <div class=\"celestial-sphere\" style=\"width: 10px; height: 10px;\">\n            <label>Earth</label>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"celestial-sphere\" style=\"width: 10.8px; height: 10.8px;\">\n            <label>Proxima Cen-b</label>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n        <table cellspacing=\"0\">\n          <tr>\n            <td>Mass</td>\n            <td>1.270 Earth masses</td>\n          </tr>\n          <tr>\n            <td>Density</td>\n            <td>5.540 grams per cubic centimeter</td>\n          </tr>\n          <tr>\n            <td>Radius</td>\n            <td>1.080 Earth radiae</td>\n          </tr>\n          <tr>\n            <td>Semi-major Axis</td>\n            <td>0.0485 AU</td>\n          </tr>\n          <tr>\n            <td>Eccentricity</td>\n            <td>0.35</td>\n          </tr>\n          <tr>\n            <td>Orbital Period</td>\n            <td>11.186 days</td>\n          </tr>\n          <tr>\n            <td>Discovery Method</td>\n            <td>Radial Velocity</td>\n          </tr>\n          <tr>\n            <td>Discovery Facility</td>\n            <td>European Southern Observatory</td>\n          </tr>\n          <tr>\n            <td>Discovery Telescope</td>\n            <td>Multiple Telescopes</td>\n          </tr>\n          <tr>\n            <td>Discovery Instrument</td>\n            <td>Multiple Instruments</td>\n          </tr>\n          <tr>\n            <td>Discovery Date</td>\n            <td>2016-08</td>\n          </tr>\n          <tr>\n            <td>Reference</td>\n            <td><a refstr=ANGLADA_ESCUD_EACUTE__ET_AL__2016 href=https://ui.adsabs.harvard.edu/abs/2016Natur.536..437A/abstract target=ref>Anglada-Escud&eacute; et al. 2016</a></td>\n          </tr>\n        </table>\n      </section>\n    </div></a>\n  ",
